    'Episodes Pubdate Date': '2015-09-15',
    'Episodes Summary': '<p>Security researchers and organizations have to stay vigilant in this cat-and-mouse game.</p><p>Shuman Ghosemajumder is the VP of Product at Shape Security, which defends applications from malware and bots. He is the former click fraud czar at Google, and he will be speaking at <a href="https://qconsf.com/?utm_source=mediapartner&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_campaign=sedaily">QCon San Francisco</a>.</p>',
