    'Episodes Summary': '<p>In this episode, I gathered questions from listeners in our Slack channel and Twitter feed. The questions I answered include:</p><p>We always want more feedback and questions. Please <a href="mailto:jeff@softwareengineeringdaily.com">email me</a>, <a href="http://softwaredaily.herokuapp.com/">join Slack</a>, and fill out <a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeCl7hrv6BgmQyMwRnoUCeUB9-p5LEsKyIr7PuDZp0kPIF5kQ/viewform?usp=sf_link">our survey</a>!</p>',
