    'Episodes Summary': '<p>Most programmers spend lots of their time reading content about software. Since our field changes so rapidly, engineers consume news and editorials voraciously, trying to keep up with the impossibly fast pace. The Practical Dev is a collection of blog posts, editorials, and interviews that was created to help with that end.</p><p>Ben Halpern is the creator of Practical Dev, and he joins the show to discuss software editorialism. The goal of the Practical Dev to help developers grow and learn, and Ben is working towards that goal by providing a platform for engineers to write long-form content.</p>',
