    'Episodes Summary': '<p>It provides automated code grading, plagiarism checking, code quality analysis and additional course management tools.</p><p>Prah Veluvolu is the CEO and Co-founder of Mimir. He studied at Purdue University and participated in the Boiler Startup Accelerator before graduating from the Y Combinator Summer 2015 class.</p>',
