    'Episodes Summary': '<p>As software engineering gets more popular, the resources that we use to read and understand software are growing and improving.</p><p><a href="http://www.scaleyourcode.com"> Scale Your Code</a> is an organization that seeks to improve accessibility to the world’s programming knowledge, and today’s guest Christophe Limpalair joins me to discuss Scale Your Code. Christophe is a podcaster and blogger who runs Scale Your Code.</p>',
