    'Episodes Pubdate Date': '2015-09-11',
    'Episodes Summary': '<p>Christopher Kelly is a computer scientist and a pro mountain biker who now works full-time as a health hacker.</p><p>He is a co-founder of Nourish Balance Thrive, where he works alongside two medical doctors, a food scientist and a registered nurse to help people feel and perform better using biomedical testing together with diet and lifestyle hacks.</p><p>At QCon San Francisco, he will be giving a talk called <a href="https://qconsf.com/sf2015/presentation/debug-me?utm_source=mediapartner&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_campaign=sedaily">Debug Me</a>.</p>',
